The gel fixes and sticks between the sands and clays. What becomes of it? Our mousse, diatoms' perfect. Now, understanding how the gel interacts with the sediments is more arduous. Just like cooking, we succeed in the recipe, but explaining how the eggs work together is another story. And that's what the next objectives of my thesis will be.
